author: jukka
msg: OAK-1417: Processing pending observation events does not scale linearly with the number of events
Shortcut NamePathMapperImpl.getJcrPath() for the common case where
there are no local namespace remappings. This removes the O(log n)
cost of each Event.getPath() call, and helps drop the observed performance
closer to O(n) than O(n log n)

author: jukka
msg: Reuse previous property records if the value(s) have not changed.
This optimizes the case where a binary value is rewritten without changes.
